  - Popular intro: Joshua Foer, *Moonwalking with Einstein: The Art and Science of Remembering* (Penguin, 2011)
  - Technical reference: **K. Anders Ericsson** et al., eds., *The Cambridge Handbook of Expertise and Expert Performance* (Cambridge UP, 2006)
